{
     "title":{
        "text":"近战兵",
        "color":"gold",
        "hover_event": {
            "action": "show_text",
            "value": "冬季战场制作组 编写"
        }
     },
     "pause": false,
     "type":"dialog_list",
     "body":[
        {
            "type":"plain_message",
            "contents":{
                "text": "近战兵：所有人都想干掉他，他从没倒下过",
                "color": "yellow"
            },
            "width": 500
        },
        {
        "type": "plain_message",
        "width": 300,
        "contents":[
            {
                "text": "盾。斧。剑。下界合金甲,最传统，也最稳。"
            }
        ]
        },
        {
        "type": "plain_message",
        "width": 300,
        "contents":[
            {
                "text": "我们们削过他多少次了？防护削过，伤害削过，地图为了针对他甚至减少室内场景——他还是能举着盾，一步一步往点里走。"
            }
        ]
        },
        {
        "type": "plain_message",
        "width": 300,
        "contents":[
            {
                "text": "他像冬战的地基,我们可以在上面盖狙击手的高塔，搭航空兵的跑道，挖雪原村庄的地下隧道——但地基就是地基。他不动，整个游戏就不散。他不是最强的。他只是从来没认输过。"
            }
        ]
        },
        {
            "type": "item",
            "width": 100,
            "item": {
                "id": "netherite_axe",
                "components": {
                    "enchantments": {
                        "efficiency":4,
                        "unbreaking":3,
                        "silk_touch":1,
                        "sharpness":100,
                        "mending":1
                    },
                    "unbreakable": {},
                    "custom_name": {
                        "translate":"djzc.heavy_axe",
                        "fallback":"普普通通的消防斧头"
                    }
                }
            }
        },
        {
            "type": "item",
            "width": 100,
            "item": {
                "id": "netherite_sword",
                "components": {
                    "enchantments": {
                        "sharpness":80,
                        "unbreaking":3,
                        "knockback":1
                    },
                    "unbreakable": {},
                    "custom_name": {
                        "translate":"djzc.heavy_sword",
                        "fallback":"近战剑"
                    }
                }
            }
        },
        {
            "type": "item",
            "width": 100,
            "item": {
                "id": "crossbow",
                "components": {
                    "enchantments": {
                        "infinity": 1,
                        "quick_charge": 5
                    },
                    "unbreakable": {},
                    "custom_name": {
                        "translate":"djzc.heavy_pistol",
                        "fallback":"近战手枪"
                    }
                }
            }
        }
     ],
     "columns": 4,
     "dialogs": [
        "djzc444:wiki/wiki_type_intro"
     ],
